### ============================================
### Blocked Entities API Tests
### اختبارات API الكيانات المحظورة
### ============================================
### Base URL: http://localhost:3006/api/admin/blocked-entities
### Required: Admin JWT Token (System Admin or Super Admin for modifications)
### ============================================

### Variables - قم بتغيير هذه القيم حسب بيئتك
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3006/api
@adminToken = YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
@entityId = 1
@entityType = user
@blockId = 1

### ============================================
### 1. AUTHENTICATION - المصادقة
### ============================================

### Login as Admin (to get token)
### تسجيل دخول كأدمن للحصول على التوكن
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth-admin/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@bashraai.com",
  "password": "your_admin_password"
}

### ============================================
### 2. READ OPERATIONS - عمليات القراءة (Any Admin)
### ============================================

### Get All Blocked Entities - جلب جميع الكيانات المحظورة
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/blocked-entities
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: ar

### Get Active Blocked Entities Only - الكيانات المحظورة النشطة فقط
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/blocked-entities?is_active=true
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: ar

### Get Removed (Inactive) Blocks - الحظر الملغي
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/blocked-entities?is_active=false
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: ar

### Filter by Entity Type - فلتر حسب نوع الكيان
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/blocked-entities?entity_type=user
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: ar

### Filter by Block Type - فلتر حسب نوع الحظر
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/blocked-entities?block_type=temporary
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: ar

### Filter Blocked Doctors - فلتر الأطباء المحظورين
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/blocked-entities?entity_type=doctor&is_active=true
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: ar

### Filter Blocked Assistants - فلتر المساعدين المحظورين
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/blocked-entities?entity_type=assistant&is_active=true
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: ar

### Filter Blocked Admins - فلتر المديرين المحظورين
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/blocked-entities?entity_type=admin&is_active=true
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: ar

### Search Blocked Entities - البحث في الكيانات المحظورة
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/blocked-entities?search=example@email.com
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: ar

### Get with Pagination - جلب مع صفحات
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/blocked-entities?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: ar

### Sort by Block Until Date - ترتيب حسب تاريخ انتهاء الحظر
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/blocked-entities?sort_by=blocked_until&sort_order=ASC
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: ar

### Combined Filters - فلاتر مجمعة
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/blocked-entities?entity_type=user&block_type=temporary&is_active=true&page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: ar

### ============================================
### 3. STATISTICS - الإحصائيات
### ============================================

### Get Block Statistics - إحصائيات الحظر
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/blocked-entities/statistics
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: ar

### ============================================
### 4. CHECK BLOCK STATUS - التحقق من حالة الحظر
### ============================================

### Check if User is Blocked - التحقق من حظر مستخدم
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/blocked-entities/check?entity_id={{entityId}}&entity_type=user
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: ar

### Check if Doctor is Blocked - التحقق من حظر طبيب
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/blocked-entities/check?entity_id=1&entity_type=doctor
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: ar

### Check if Assistant is Blocked - التحقق من حظر مساعد
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/blocked-entities/check?entity_id=1&entity_type=assistant
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: ar

### Check if Admin is Blocked - التحقق من حظر أدمن
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/blocked-entities/check?entity_id=1&entity_type=admin
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: ar

### ============================================
### 5. BLOCK DETAILS - تفاصيل الحظر
### ============================================

### Get Block Details by ID - تفاصيل الحظر بالمعرف
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/blocked-entities/{{blockId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: ar

### ============================================
### 6. BLOCK HISTORY - سجل الحظر
### ============================================

### Get User Block History - سجل حظر مستخدم
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/blocked-entities/history/user/{{entityId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: ar

### Get Doctor Block History - سجل حظر طبيب
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/blocked-entities/history/doctor/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: ar

### Get Assistant Block History - سجل حظر مساعد
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/blocked-entities/history/assistant/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: ar

### Get Admin Block History - سجل حظر أدمن
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/blocked-entities/history/admin/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: ar

### ============================================
### 7. BLOCK ENTITY - حظر كيان (System Admin+)
### ============================================

### Block User - Temporary - حظر مستخدم مؤقتاً
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/blocked-entities/block
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: ar

{
  "entity_id": 1,
  "entity_type": "user",
  "block_type": "temporary",
  "blocked_until": "2025-02-15T00:00:00.000Z",
  "reason": "مخالفة سياسات الاستخدام - تم التحذير مسبقاً ولم يتم الالتزام"
}

### Block User - Permanent - حظر مستخدم دائم
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/blocked-entities/block
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: ar

{
  "entity_id": 2,
  "entity_type": "user",
  "block_type": "permanent",
  "reason": "انتهاك خطير لسياسات المنصة - حساب مزيف"
}

### Block User - Warning - تحذير مستخدم
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/blocked-entities/block
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: ar

{
  "entity_id": 3,
  "entity_type": "user",
  "block_type": "warning",
  "reason": "تحذير أول بسبب سلوك غير لائق في المحادثات"
}

### Block Doctor - Temporary - حظر طبيب مؤقتاً
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/blocked-entities/block
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: ar

{
  "entity_id": 1,
  "entity_type": "doctor",
  "block_type": "temporary",
  "blocked_until": "2025-01-30T00:00:00.000Z",
  "reason": "شكاوى متعددة من المرضى - يتم التحقيق في الأمر"
}

### Block Doctor - Permanent - حظر طبيب دائم
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/blocked-entities/block
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: ar

{
  "entity_id": 2,
  "entity_type": "doctor",
  "block_type": "permanent",
  "reason": "تقديم معلومات طبية خاطئة ومضللة للمرضى"
}

### Block Assistant - حظر مساعد
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/blocked-entities/block
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: ar

{
  "entity_id": 1,
  "entity_type": "assistant",
  "block_type": "temporary",
  "blocked_until": "2025-01-20T00:00:00.000Z",
  "reason": "عدم الالتزام بمواعيد العمل المحددة"
}

### Block Admin (Super Admin Only) - حظر أدمن
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/blocked-entities/block
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: ar

{
  "entity_id": 2,
  "entity_type": "admin",
  "block_type": "permanent",
  "reason": "إساءة استخدام صلاحيات الأدمن"
}

### ============================================
### 8. UNBLOCK ENTITY - إلغاء حظر كيان (System Admin+)
### ============================================

### Unblock User - إلغاء حظر مستخدم
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/blocked-entities/unblock
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: ar

{
  "entity_id": 1,
  "entity_type": "user",
  "reason": "تم مراجعة الحالة وإلغاء الحظر بعد التزام المستخدم"
}

### Unblock Doctor - إلغاء حظر طبيب
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/blocked-entities/unblock
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: ar

{
  "entity_id": 1,
  "entity_type": "doctor",
  "reason": "تم التحقق من الشكاوى وثبت عدم صحتها"
}

### Unblock Assistant - إلغاء حظر مساعد
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/blocked-entities/unblock
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: ar

{
  "entity_id": 1,
  "entity_type": "assistant",
  "reason": "تم الالتزام بالتعليمات"
}

### Unblock Admin (Super Admin Only) - إلغاء حظر أدمن
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/blocked-entities/unblock
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: ar

{
  "entity_id": 2,
  "entity_type": "admin",
  "reason": "تم مراجعة الحالة"
}

### ============================================
### 9. UPDATE BLOCK - تحديث سجل الحظر (System Admin+)
### ============================================

### Extend Temporary Block - تمديد الحظر المؤقت
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/blocked-entities/{{blockId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: ar

{
  "blocked_until": "2025-03-01T00:00:00.000Z",
  "reason": "تم تمديد فترة الحظر بسبب عدم الاستجابة"
}

### Convert Temporary to Permanent - تحويل مؤقت إلى دائم
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/blocked-entities/{{blockId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: ar

{
  "block_type": "permanent",
  "blocked_until": null,
  "reason": "تحويل إلى حظر دائم بسبب تكرار المخالفات"
}

### Update Block Reason Only - تحديث السبب فقط
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/blocked-entities/{{blockId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: ar

{
  "reason": "تم تحديث سبب الحظر بعد مراجعة إضافية"
}

### Convert to Warning - تحويل إلى تحذير
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/blocked-entities/{{blockId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: ar

{
  "block_type": "warning",
  "reason": "تم تخفيف العقوبة إلى تحذير"
}

### ============================================
### 10. BULK OPERATIONS - عمليات مجمعة (System Admin+)
### ============================================

### Bulk Block Users - حظر مجموعة مستخدمين
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/blocked-entities/bulk/block
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: ar

{
  "entities": [
    { "entity_id": 1, "entity_type": "user" },
    { "entity_id": 2, "entity_type": "user" },
    { "entity_id": 3, "entity_type": "user" }
  ],
  "block_type": "temporary",
  "blocked_until": "2025-02-01T00:00:00.000Z",
  "reason": "حظر جماعي بسبب نشاط مشبوه تم رصده"
}

### Bulk Block Mixed Entities - حظر مجموعة متنوعة
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/blocked-entities/bulk/block
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: ar

{
  "entities": [
    { "entity_id": 1, "entity_type": "user" },
    { "entity_id": 1, "entity_type": "doctor" },
    { "entity_id": 1, "entity_type": "assistant" }
  ],
  "block_type": "warning",
  "reason": "تحذير جماعي بسبب مخالفة سياسات المنصة"
}

### Bulk Block Permanent - حظر جماعي دائم
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/blocked-entities/bulk/block
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: ar

{
  "entities": [
    { "entity_id": 4, "entity_type": "user" },
    { "entity_id": 5, "entity_type": "user" }
  ],
  "block_type": "permanent",
  "reason": "حسابات مزيفة تم التأكد منها"
}

### Bulk Unblock Users - إلغاء حظر مجموعة مستخدمين
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/blocked-entities/bulk/unblock
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: ar

{
  "entities": [
    { "entity_id": 1, "entity_type": "user" },
    { "entity_id": 2, "entity_type": "user" }
  ],
  "reason": "إلغاء حظر جماعي بعد مراجعة الحالات"
}

### Bulk Unblock Mixed Entities - إلغاء حظر مجموعة متنوعة
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/blocked-entities/bulk/unblock
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: ar

{
  "entities": [
    { "entity_id": 1, "entity_type": "user" },
    { "entity_id": 1, "entity_type": "doctor" }
  ],
  "reason": "إلغاء حظر جماعي"
}

### ============================================
### 11. AUTO-UNBLOCK - إلغاء الحظر التلقائي
### ============================================

### Auto-Unblock Expired Temporary Blocks
### إلغاء حظر الكيانات المنتهية تلقائياً
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/blocked-entities/auto-unblock
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept-Language: ar

