### ============================================
### WORKFLOW EXAMPLES - أمثلة سير العمل
### ============================================

### === Workflow 1: Block User for Violation ===
### Step 1: Check if user is already blocked
# GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/blocked-entities/check?entity_id=5&entity_type=user

### Step 2: Block the user
# POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/blocked-entities/block
# Body: { "entity_id": 5, "entity_type": "user", "block_type": "temporary", "blocked_until": "2025-02-01", "reason": "..." }

### Step 3: Verify block was created
# GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/blocked-entities?entity_type=user&is_active=true

### === Workflow 2: Handle Appeal ===
### Step 1: Get user's block history
# GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/blocked-entities/history/user/5

### Step 2: Review and decide to unblock
# POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/blocked-entities/unblock
# Body: { "entity_id": 5, "entity_type": "user", "reason": "Appeal accepted" }

### === Workflow 3: Escalate Warning to Block ===
### Step 1: Find existing warning
# GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/blocked-entities?entity_type=user&block_type=warning&is_active=true

### Step 2: Update to temporary block
# PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/blocked-entities/:blockId
# Body: { "block_type": "temporary", "blocked_until": "2025-02-01", "reason": "Escalated from warning" }

### === Workflow 4: Daily Cleanup ===
### Run auto-unblock for expired temporary blocks
# POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/blocked-entities/auto-unblock
